<http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ref/2333088//items/ZRQLQ8CL> a ipbes:Reference ;
    ipbes:Chapter <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ch/PPA16ch2>,
        <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ch/PPA16ch3> ;
    ipbes:Report <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/PPA16> ;
