<http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ref/2333088//items/ZL2MI77F> a ipbes:Reference ;
    ipbes:Chapter <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ch/PPA16ch2>,
        <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ch/PPA16ch5>,
        <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/ch/PPA16ch6> ;
    ipbes:Report <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/PPA16> ;
    ipbes:SubChapter <http://ontology.ipbes.net/report/sch/PPA16-2.3>,
